{
  "stem": "25651.8",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were the people who passively resisted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you passively resist, we'll get rid of you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But how do you get rid of men who are-- you-- I mean, you know, you don't tell people you're going to gas them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they already knew that there were gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Freddy must've known, because he committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there's all kinds of talk that they were planning a revolt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Freddy was supposed to be the leader of the revolt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he didn't do it because he was a coward.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's the sort of story that was created in Czechoslovakia under the communist regime to discredit Zionist leadership and Zionist youth movements because the policy of the communists became anti-Zionist.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It-- it's very invidious how prevalent the opinions are anti-Freddy amongst Czech Jews who have been subjected for 50 years to this communist propaganda.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Even today, you know, people sort of hear what was being said in the '50s.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Propaganda is a very-- very powerful thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, [? where ?] [? we are, ?] that's-- oh, I'm digressing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "These men were loaded onto lorries.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were told that they were going to an Arbeitslager.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they went on a journey all night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they arrived in the morning back in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were told they were somewhere in Poland and going to a sauna and schnell, schnell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now they were without sleep all night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were sort of conditioned by being told over several days how they were going to this Arbeitslager, you see?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they were being driven all around Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I was told this by the-- by the Sonderkommando, who worked in the crematoria, by a friend of mine called Galen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'll tell you about Galen in a little while.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
